			<br><br>

			<<link [[Comfort (1:00)|Home Comfort]]>><<famegood 1>><<pass 60>><<hope 1>><</link>><<ghope>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Ignore|Orphanage]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
			<br>

		<<case 2>>
